title: Facebook talking to U.S. regulators about crypto offering: report
text: Facebook Inc. has been in contact with the Commodity Futures Trading Commission -- the top U.S. regulator for futures and derivatives -- as it plans to roll out a digital currency

title: Facebook in talks with U.S. derivatives regulator over digital currency plans: FT
text: Facebook Inc is in talks with the U.S. derivatives regulator, the Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC), over the social media company's plans for a digital currency, the Financial Times reported on Sunday.
